title: Dakine Excursion Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Excursion Glove.
Features: 
- Insert: Gore Tex® Waterproof / Breathable insert
- Insulation: Primaloft® [ 170g ]
- Palm: Durable water repellent leather
- Shell: Durable water repellent leather / 4 way stretch soft shell
- Lining: 360g wool lining
- Cuff Closure: Adjustable hook and loop
